      {"@type":"Question","name":"Which app is best for paying utility bills in Pakistan?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"JazzCash is the most widely used app with coverage for all WAPDA DISCOs, K-Electric, SNGPL, SSGC, PTCL, and WASA. It charges zero service fee for most bills. Easypaisa is equally good and has stronger agent coverage in rural areas. For bank users, HBL Mobile and MCB Mobile offer the same utility bill payment feature."}},
